overview.longBusinessSummary: LuxExperience B.V., through its subsidiary, operates an online shopping platform in Germany, the United States, rest of Europe, and internationally. The company offers womenswear, menswear, kidswear, fine jewelry, watches, and lifestyle products under the Mytheresa, NET-A-PORTER, MR PORTER, YOOX, and the OUTNET brand name. The company was formerly known as MYT Netherlands Parent B.V. and changed its name to LuxExperience B.V. in May 2025. LuxExperience B.V. was founded in 1987 and is based in Munich, Germany.
